quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  8,62,"Tí wọ́n bá tún fẹ́ tàn ọ́ jẹ, dájúdájú Allāhu á tó ọ. Òun ni Ẹni tí Ó fi àrànṣe Rẹ̀ àti àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo ràn ọ́ lọ́wọ́.",""
  8,63,"Allāhu pa ọkàn wọn pọ̀ mọ́ra wọn. Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé o ná gbogbo n̄ǹkan tí ń bẹ lórí ilẹ̀ pátápátá, ìwọ kò lè pa ọkàn wọn pọ̀ mọ́ra wọn. Ṣùgbọ́n Allāhu pa ọkàn wọn pọ̀ mọ́ra wọn, dájúdájú Òun ni Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n.",""
  8,64,"Ìwọ Ànábì, Allāhu ti tó ìwọ àti àwọn tó tẹ̀lé ọ nínú àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo.",""
  8,65,"Ìwọ Ànábì, gba àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo ní ìyànjú lórí ogun ẹ̀sìn. Tí ogún onísùúrù bá wà nínú yín, wọn yóò borí igba. Tí ọgọ́rùn-ún bá sì wà nínú yín, wọn yóò borí ẹgbẹ̀rún nínú àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nítorí pé dájúdájú wọ́n jẹ́ ìjọ tí kò gbọ́ àgbọ́yé.",""
  8,66,"Nísisìn yìí, Allāhu ti ṣe é ní fífúyẹ́ fún yín. Ó sì mọ̀ pé dájúdájú àìlágbára ń bẹ fún yín. Nítorí náà, tí ọgọ́rùn-ún onísùúrù bá wà nínú yín, wọn yóò borí igba. Tí ẹgbẹ̀rún kan bá sì wà nínú yín, wọn yóò borí ẹgbẹ̀rún méjì pẹ̀lú àṣẹ Allāhu. Allāhu sì wà pẹ̀lú àwọn onísùúrù.",""
  8,67,"Kò yẹ fún Ànábì kan láti ní ẹrú ogun títí ọwọ́ rẹ̀ máa fi ba àwọn ọ̀tá rẹ̀ lórí ilẹ̀ dáadáa ní ti pípa.<sup>1</sup> Ẹ̀yin ń fẹ́ ìgbádùn ayé, Allāhu sì ń fẹ́ ọ̀run. Allāhu sì ni Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n.","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Gọ̄fir; 40:55."
  8,68,"Tí kì í bá ṣe ti àkọsílẹ̀ kan tó ti gbawájú láti ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu ni, ọwọ́ ìyà ńlá kò bá tẹ̀ yín nípa n̄ǹkan tí ẹ gbà (ní owó ìtúsílẹ̀).",""
  8,69,"Nítorí náà, ẹ jẹ nínú ohun tí ẹ kó ní ọrọ̀ ogun (tí ó jẹ́) ẹ̀tọ́ (àti) n̄ǹkan dáadáa. Kí ẹ sì bẹ̀rù Allāhu. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run.",""
